    ∀ G : SimpleGraph (Fin (b ^ k)), HasControlBlockModularBucketingWitnessOfCard G (M * k)

/--
Bounded multiblock modular bucketing target: the modular bucketing data uses at most `r k`
control blocks at scale `k`.
-/
